{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for relentless action in a top-down zombie shooter that blends strategic gameplay with survival against endless waves of zombies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Position yourself wisely, manage your resources, and rely on skillful play to survive the onslaught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/strategy_optimized.gif?t=1738931857\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>End-of-Wave Buffs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After each wave, choose from powerful buffs to tailor your playstyle and counter the increasing threats. Inspired by survivors-like mechanics, these upgrades can turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/buffgif_optimized.gif?t=1738931857\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dynamic Arsenal</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Between waves, open the shop to gear up. Purchase weapons, ammo, and equipment to stay ahead of the zombie onslaught and prepare for what\u2019s next. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/extras/shopgif_optimized.gif?t=1738931857\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Offline Singleplayer &amp; Co-op multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play solo in offline mode without requiring internet connection or team up with other players in multiplayer mode.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738931857","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042050/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738931857","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam